This is an Expo/React Native mobile application.

Framework information:
- Built with Expo managed workflow
- Uses React Native for cross-platform mobile development
- Follows React Native and Expo best practices and conventions
- Use useThemeColor hook to get colors to use for styling

Key technologies:
- JavaScript/TypeScript
- React Native components and APIs
- Expo SDK and features
- React Navigation for routing
- React Native styling and layout with Flexbox

File structure conventions:
- /src - Main source code directory
- /assets - Images, fonts, and other static assets
- /components - Reusable React Native components
- /screens - Screen components for different app views
- /navigation - Navigation configuration
- /services - API calls and business logic
- /utils - Helper functions and utilities
- /hooks - Custom React hooks
- /constants - App-wide constants and theme settings

Build and deployment:
- Uses Expo CLI for development and building
- Can be built for iOS and Android platforms
- Supports Expo Go for development testing
- Can be published to Expo's servers or built as standalone apps

Development environment:
- Node.js
- npm/yarn package manager
- Expo CLI tools
- iOS Simulator / Android Emulator for testing
